cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.RO, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically stereo image deblurring. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves depth estimation and fusion of two views, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of unmanned aerial vehicles could also suggest cs.RO (Robotics) as a possible sub-category. Finally, the proposed network involves deep learning, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
